{"tid":1737944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【理工大學「抗爭飯堂」 他要緊守崗位到最後一刻】","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:05:22.000Z","uid":50535,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"282ced270f5171e7ee24ece66a867a572a67449d","tid":1737944,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞讚好專頁<br />\n26分鐘 &middot; <br />\n【理工大學「抗爭飯堂」 他要緊守崗位到最後一刻】<br />\n<br />\n在理工大學的「抗爭飯堂」，有廚師繼續在處理食材，為仍然留在校園內的人準備午飯。<br />\n<br />\n廚師仍然願意接受訪問，表示會一直留守廚房，直至警察最終進入校園、阻止他煮飯，他也會想盡辦法趕走警察。廚師表示，不擔心被圍困，「走唔到咪好囉！持續抗爭囉！戰鬥到底囉！ 走嚟做乜撚嘢呀！走就唔出嚟啦！」<br />\n<br />\n他又自稱「暴徒」，自己的「魔法」就在廚房進行。會否擔心被控告暴動？「我係暴動吖嘛！唔認暴動啲人就咪撚出嚟啦！我係煮緊飯暴動呀！拉鳩我十年（監禁）吖笨！」<br />\n<br />\n記者問他是否只是負責煮飯，廚師則表示：「都仲有揼垃圾架！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，廚師最終因與記者談話分神，焗爐中的香腸不幸被焗燶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7faa1d07ccdf460c8735fa096db5b12d09484bb","tid":1737944,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入----------&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d5688529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"99e53769f3dae7b636ef5c1c071239096ec5fc6a","tid":1737944,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:54